      • registerMyNameInBStats

        public abstract void registerMyNameInBStats(String name)
        Sends the given name at BStats.

        The name should be the name of the plugin using UneiConfiguration.

        This is purely optional, it's mainly to see how many plugin is using our API.

        Parameters:
        name - The name of the plugin depending on UneiConfiguration.

      • checkVersion

        public abstract IUpdater.Result checkVersion()
        Synchronously check for a new version of UneiConfiguration.

        This is the same as calling IUpdater.checkVersion().

        Returns:
        IUpdater.Result#UPDATE_AVAILABLE if an update is available ;
        IUpdater.Result#NO_UPDATE if you the latest version ;
        IUpdater.Result#FAILED if the updater was unable to check for a newer version.

      • checkVerionAsync

        public abstract void checkVerionAsync(IUpdater.ICallback callback)
        Asynchronously check for a new version of UneiConfiguration.

        This is the same as calling IUpdater.checkVersionAsync(me.unei.configuration.plugin.IUpdater.ICallback).

        Parameters:
        callback - The callback witch will be called upon version check completion.
        See Also:
        checkVersion()
